Coding standards

*************** Components naming **************
Each component will be named writing the key that represents the component, followed by the name of the component,
according to the list bellowed, each component should be shown like this:

Forms ---> frm + name in camel Case... Example: frmMenu
Buttons ---> btn + name in camel Case... Example: btnOrders
Labels ---> lbl + name in camel Case... Example: lblOrders
TextBoxes ---> tb + name in camel Case... Example: tbPrice
ComboBoxes ---> cb + name in camel Case... Example: cbProducts
DataGridViews ---> dgv + name in camel Case... Example: dgvActiveOrders

